iệc hủy giao dịch qua đường dây nóng 0967070790\r\n\r\n- Trả lại hàng hoá đã nhận nhưng chưa sử dụng hoặc hưởng bất kỳ lợi ích nào từ hàng hóa đó (theo quy định của chính sách đổi trả hàng).\r\n\r\n</div>','Điều khoản dịch vụ','','inherit','closed','closed','','258-revision-v1','','','2019-08-25 09:11:34','2019-08-25 09:11:34','',258,'http://xaydung4.muathemewordpress.net/258-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(567,1,'2019-08-25 14:47:50','2019-08-25 14:47:50',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','567','','','2019-08-25 14:47:50','2019-08-25 14:47:50','',0,'http://xaydung4.muathemewordpress.net/?p=567',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(568,1,'2019-08-25 14:47:50','2019-08-25 14:47:50','','Quy định sử dụng','','publish','closed','closed','','quy-dinh-su-dung','','','2019-08-25 14:47:50','2019-08-25 14:47:50','',0,'http://xaydung4.muathemewordpress.net/?p=568',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(569,1,'2019-08-25 14:47:50','2019-08-25 14:47:50','','Chính sách vận chuyển','','publish','closed','closed','','chinh-sach-van-chuyen','','','2019-08-25 14:47:50','2019-08-25 14:47:50','',0,'http://xaydung4.muathemewordpress.net/?p=569',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(570,1,'2019-08-25 14:47:50','2019-08-25 14:47:50','','Chính sách đổi trả','','publish','closed','closed','','chinh-sach-doi-tra','','','2019-08-25 14:47:50','2019-08-25 14:47:50','',0,'http://xaydung4.muathemewordpress.net/?p=570',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(571,1,'2019-08-25 14:48:26','2019-08-25 14:48:26',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','571','','','2019-08-25 14:48:26','2019-08-25 14:48:26','',0,'http://xaydung4.muathemewordpress.net/?p=571',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(572,1,'2019-08-25 14:48:26','2019-08-25 14:48:26',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','572','','','2019-08-25 14:48:26','2019-08-25 14:48:26','',0,'http://xaydung4.muathemewordpress.net/?p=572',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(573,1,'2019-08-25 14:48:26','2019-08-25 14:48:26','','Hướng dẫn thanh toán','','publish','closed','closed','','huong-dan-thanh-toan','','','2019-